Other: Henderson Insurance will send a letter confirming they are on risk and investigating, and will need to speak to the Farrells first.

Liability Summary:
The Farrells may have liability regardless of who was walking the dog at the time, as they are the dog owners. Henderson Insurance's policy includes personal liability cover, but they will need to take instructions from the Farrells on how to proceed.
